          alt="News Image"
        >

        <div class="card-content">

          <div class="card-tag">News</div>

          <div class="card-title">
            Major Product Launch Expected This Week
          </div>

          <div class="card-desc">
            Stay informed with the newest announcements and platform developments happening across the industry.
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="card">

        <img 
          class="card-image"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516321318423-f06f85e504b3?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="News Image"
        >

        <div class="card-content">

          <div class="card-tag">News</div>

          <div class="card-title">
            New Feature Rollout Begins Globally
          </div>

          <div class="card-desc">
            Early users are already testing improved workflows and redesigned navigation systems.
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="card">

        <img 
          class="card-image"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520607162513-77705c0f0d4a?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="News Image"
        >

        <div class="card-content">

          <div class="card-tag">News</div>

          <div class="card-title">
            Community Reactions Continue Growing Online
          </div>

          <div class="card-desc">
            Thousands of users are sharing feedback and discussing upcoming updates across multiple channels.
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- REVIEWS -->

  <div class="tab-content" id="reviews">

    <div class="cards">

      <div class="card">

        <img 
          class="card-image"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516321497487-e288fb19713f?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Expert Review"
        >

        <div class="card-content">

          <div class="card-tag">Expert Reviews</div>

          <div class="card-title">
            Analysts Praise the New Interface Design
          </div>

          <div class="card-desc">
            Experts highlight cleaner layouts, improved accessibility and smoother overall user experience.
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="card">

        <img 
          class="card-image"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Expert Review"
        >

        <div class="card-content">

          <div class="card-tag">Expert Reviews</div>

          <div class="card-title">
            Performance Improvements Tested in Real Usage
          </div>

          <div class="card-desc">
            Benchmarks show noticeable gains in responsiveness and stability across devices.
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="card">

        <img 
          class="card-image"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop"
